parameters: [Coris] You are Luna, the blue mage from Sheena Village...!
[Coris] I am 'Coris', the leader of the resistance in this village.
Ceres: "Luna, we'll also try searching for Regnus Grahardt."
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Luna, it seems you've somehow become able to use magic. I'm surprised.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] I've come to give you a warning.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] If you continue to interfere with me, you'll regret it.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] If you behave, you won't have to die.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Lucia, you've ordered the generals of Valentina to deliberately attack
civilians, haven't you?
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] It's because you and your resistance keep foolishly opposing us.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] If you continue this senseless slaughter, I will use whatever means necessary
to kill you.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] Have you forgotten that you couldn't do it before? It's impossible for you.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Black Witch, Lucia. Even if we are direct descendants of sorcerers, we will not
give up. We will not allow any more slaughter and tyranny.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] I am the "Core" of black magic and the progenitor. And I am the princess of
this country.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] To a direct descendant sorcerer like me, even a sorcerer with innate talent
pales in comparison.

\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] I'm talking about you, Luna. At the prestigious Valentina Magic School, you
were a student who caught Sylvia's eye. But your magical talent is nothing
compared to mine.
\C[17][Lucia]\C[0] To someone with the power of a direct lineage like myself.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] I will definitely find Regnus Grahardt.
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] Luna, what are we going to do now?

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Let's head back to Sheena Village for now. I'm worried about Noah's leg
necrosis.
\C[24][Becky]\C[0] Yes, that sounds like a good idea.
